Author: judgejudystan
Text: I agree so much! It takes so much effort for me to stop when I’m full. And thank you so much :)

Author: raverae
Text: It’s literally a goal to stop eating before you’re so uncomfortably full. I do it all the time . I know I should stop eating but the food is so good. It’s just that split second where I decide I should stop eating that seems so hard but when I actually stop it feels like such an accomplishment and it is!! Proud of u!!
